How It Works

At D.Dots, we employ fully homomorphic encryption (FHE) to revolutionize the confidentiality of your data. Unlike traditional encryption that must be decrypted for any computation, our advanced FHE methods ensure that your data remains encrypted during the entire analytical process, mitigating the risk of exposure and maintaining privacy integrity.
